      133.34,
      149.93,
      203.06,
      161.4
    ],
    "text": "(CHAPTER 436)",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman-SC700"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      177.13,
      290.71,
      202.2
    ],
    "text": "BE it enacted by the Parliament of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka as follows :-",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      217.67,
      290.7,
      243.0
    ],
    "text": "1. This Act may be cited as the Rubber Control (Amendment) Act, No. 16 of 2025.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      258.47,
      290.71,
      324.6
    ],
    "text": "2. (1) The Rubber Control Act (Chapter 436) (hereinafter referred to as the \u201cprincipal enactment\u201d) is hereby amended by the substitution for the words, \u201cController\u201d and \u201cRubber Controller\u201d wherever such words appear in the principal enactment of the words, \u201cDirector-General\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      340.33,
      290.71,
      419.8
    ],
    "text": "(2) Every reference to the \u201cController\u201d and \u201cRubber Controller\u201d in any other written law or in any notice, notification, contract, communication, form, other instrument or document shall from and after the date of commencement of this Act be read and construed as a reference made to the \u201cDirector-General of the Rubber Development Department\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      435.27,
      290.7,
      460.6
    ],
    "text": "3. Section 26 of the principal enactment is hereby repealed.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      48.2,
      483.07,
      290.7,
      522.6
    ],
    "text": "4. The heading appearing immediately after the words and figures \u201cPART VI\u201d of the principal enactment is hereby repealed and the following heading substituted therefor: -",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      96.67,
      539.13,
      239.72,
      550.6
    ],
    "text": "\u201cRUBBER ADVISORY BOARD\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      300.13,
      484.05,
      360.86,
      523.37
    ],
    "text": "Replacement of heading in Part VI of the principal enactment",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      133.16,
      44.71,
      323.06,
      70.36
    ],
    "text": "Rubber Control (Amendment)Act, No. 16 of 20252",
    "fonts": [
      "MinionPro-Regular",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      131.53,
      81.74,
      374.04,
      107.47
    ],
    "text": "5. Sections 36, 37, 38, 39, 39a and 50 of the principal enactment are hereby repealed.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman",
      "Times-Roman-SC700"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      7.0,
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      131.53,
      148.74,
      374.03,
      188.47
    ],
    "text": "6. Section 52 of the principal enactment is hereby amended by the repeal of the definition of \u201cController\u201d, and the substitution therefor, of the following new definition :-",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      155.53,
      205.0,
      374.03,
      244.47
    ],
    "text": "\u201c\u201cDirector-General\u201d means the Director-General of the Rubber Development Department, appointed or deemed to have been appointed under this Act;\u201d.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      131.53,
      260.74,
      374.03,
      286.47
    ],
    "text": "7. In the event of any inconsistency between the Sinhala and Tamil texts of this Act, the Sinhala text shall prevail.",
    "fonts": [
      "Times-Bold",
      "Times-Roman"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      10.0
    ]
  },
